{"tid":1510358,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"誰是真暴徒？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-08-27T07:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T07:09:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0e058abc71bb598df05d8da0a844c585ac1f3c","tid":1510358,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190827/20756358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756358&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi4Xq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=122c54e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756358&h=d02ac397\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190827/20756358</a><br />\n<br />\n誰是真暴徒？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190827/large/1566806511_b336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190827%2Flarge%2F1566806511_b336.jpg&h=98d29f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朋友在一間充滿藍絲的公司工作，今天一上班，聽到全體同事怒斥示威者野蠻，毀壞公物，打爛麻雀館，追住警車打，非常暴力，是暴徒，警察開槍對付暴徒，是應該的。這些藍絲是土生土長香港人，五十出頭，享受過香港受法治保護的美好時代，是所謂的既得利益者。這些人，眼見香港的文明與法治不再，不是心痛香港淪喪，而是倒果為因，痛斥示威者破壞他們在溫水中被煮的生活&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我只聽朋友轉述幾句，已經肺都氣炸，想像一下她在那樣的環境中工作，對住一群是非不分、沒有靈魂、麻木不仁的同事，真替她可憐。<br />\n<br />\n示威者是暴徒？這些話若出自牆內天天看假新聞的中國人之口，我只能搖頭嘆息。但出自生活在香港，每天看得到真新聞，兩個多月來，目睹香港人怎樣由最和平最文明最理性的示威走到今天不得不在暴力鎮壓下自衛反抗的整個過程的香港人之口，實在是無法原諒的。<br />\n<br />\n老實說，我看到示威者拉倒智慧燈柱，拆開內部零件，踢爆其中藍牙傳送系統供應商與上海開發官方天網監控系統屬同一公司時，感恩之情無法言表，他們不惜賠上自己的自由、前途，甚至生命，讓我們所有的人暫免被監控、被置於一個大監獄的恐懼，讓我們暫獲自由。坐享其成者居然怒斥這些奮力反抗暴政的人？<br />\n<br />\n公然毀約，踐踏一國兩制的承諾，在香港實施極權統治的政府，居然還有一群擁護者？誰是真暴徒？所有擁護暴政的人，都是真暴徒。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n當警察開槍是克制 (曾志豪)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n青山公路行行重行行 (鄧達智)"},{"pid":"fc3244a2a33905a648e01f8f77fd4f0000757a23","tid":1510358,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi4Xq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=68aa7162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi4Xq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=01aa24ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi4Xq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=f6aac90b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"b43cdd2bb8f89456b018e2af5bc64dd2ce08e6e0","tid":1510358,"uid":149653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:01:23.000Z","msg":"我要贏呂麗乳搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6dbdfd72600e62dd144e8678456205378501e6","tid":1510358,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"我要贏呂麗乳搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2b20144158fe74440eff03566b1d8eff7b48ab","tid":1510358,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl